column2: SELECT p.objId as objid, p.ra,p.dec,p.petror9#_r,s.z, n.sersic_n, rc.MP2# as avgsurfbright, e.EW_H5_# as h5width,  e.EW_He_# as hewidth, e.EW_Hb_# as hbwidth, e.EW_Ha_# as hawidth, m.DL FROM galaxy AS p    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid    JOIN nsatlas AS n ON n.mjd = s.mjd and n.fiberID = s.fiberID and n.plate = s.plate    JOIN emissionLinesPort AS e ON e.mjd = s.mjd and e.fiberID = s.fiberID and e.plate = s.plate    JOIN RC3 AS rc ON rc.objid = p.objid    JOIN mangaPipe3D AS m  WHERE n.sersic_n < #
